{"tid":294021,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"十二年半之生雞用到變燒雞","createTime":"2017-06-22T15:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T15:16:29.000Z","uid":62067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"013a5c179fea312581b3c16af6f2179ff6313518","tid":294021,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"十二年半之生雞用到變燒雞<br />\n<br />\n用咗十二年半仲咁靚仔乾淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/854228b56c27cbb41ee7332a8c4c905d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F854228b56c27cbb41ee7332a8c4c905d.jpg&h=af5aa46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反轉個雞肚...<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/bbc58236594102468d7781b552e29889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fbbc58236594102468d7781b552e29889.jpg&h=b08662c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n燶咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/c6be02b9f0f9aaaa8f8f9dbab7630733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fc6be02b9f0f9aaaa8f8f9dbab7630733.jpg&h=0ed98ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，由2004年12月31日買返嚟至2005年1月1日正式使用，經歷不斷長時間使用直至2017年6月21日，終於因機件故障停止服役。故障前我聞到燶味，但唔知邊度燒着嘢。拆開機箱再着機一看，「咦! 點解個隻生雞HDD底部有盞燈閃吓閃吓嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」同時都聞到燶味。原來HDD個底板燒着咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   我立刻抆咗個插蘇，同時疑感可唔可以倒返D資料出嚟。今晚試咗原來係得嘅，燒雞仲可以用但我而家唔敢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲試過一次隻IBM HDD突然死亡，完全唔可以抄返D DATA出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘絕人寰"},{"pid":"3d39b0685520341641ece0394581578113cb0332","tid":294021,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"終極廣告文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n憑呢個post絕對值得換過隻新雞比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d364fcc571c7a5e69c7538707e106711cd9bc0","tid":294021,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"80G用12年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5920f324268d02d614aa395741641417e7b8972c","tid":294021,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"其實點解各位巴絲D HDD咁快死?  我唔會成日搬個機箱周圍走，又唔會揼隻HDD，WHY<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲有兩隻IDE嘅，超過十五年，一隻QUANTUM，一隻死雞，當外置用同BT裝垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aecaf007843e3e3a78480b65276b16789948b4d","tid":294021,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>80G用12年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過應該離死期不遠矣，我當佢擺個TEMP FOLDER裝BROWSER CACHE，個FIREFOX開多幾個TAB就會HANG，而家轉咗新D嘅HDD暫時冇喱個問題"},{"pid":"eb0e872204c19e88ac8f625ba3d61671462c4238","tid":294021,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"Samsung ssd 可用60年"},{"pid":"663d04d29b17bef1a95c2f09d56f3c12b239e2d8","tid":294021,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Samsung ssd 可用60年</blockquote><br />\n過咗六十年仲有人用先講"}]}